flowchart LR
  U[Usuario no navegador] --> V[Vercel Edge/CDN]
  V --> N[Next.js App Router]
  N --> RH[Route Handlers e Server Actions]
  RH --> AUTH[Auth custom: nome + senha + cookie httpOnly]
  RH --> DB[(Postgres)]
  RH --> CACHE[(Cache de jogos e selecoes)]
  CRON[Vercel Cron] --> SYNC[/api/admin/sync-worldcup]
  SYNC --> PROVIDER[API de futebol: Sportmonks/API-Football/football-data.org]
  SYNC --> FLAGS[FlagCDN/REST Countries]
  PROVIDER --> SYNC
  FLAGS --> SYNC
  SYNC --> CACHE
  CACHE --> DB
  DB --> RH
